OKbe5Eq8&h=f6acefa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8B%92%E8%B3%BC%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%85%A4%E7%82%AD-%E7%B5%82%E9%9C%80%E5%BE%9E%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%AB%98%E5%83%B9%E8%B3%BC%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%85%A4/?fbclid=IwAR3CcaVaT2AQ7j6sUyhjlwppJUU3PbtjywZ5rgX1L0IWaO6sneaOKbe5Eq8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://News.com.au\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNews.com.au&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=70c3df1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">News.com.au</a> 引述煤礦企業 Whitehaven Coal 季度報告指，中國雖改從其他國家購買煤炭，但實際上購得的仍屬澳洲煤炭。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲煤炭亦覓得新市場：「沒有中國市場後，澳洲煤炭改為出口至印度、巴基斯坦及中東市場。然而出口到這些地方的煤炭，傳統上最終目的地也會是中國。」<br />\n<br />\n澳洲媒體 ABC 新聞報道，中國向來佔紐卡素港出口煤約兩成份額，在中國禁令後，市場以為出口數字會急速下跌，但去年 12 月的數字顯示，僅較前年下跌 3%，總出口量為 1,490 萬噸煤炭。"},{"pid":"21ccd0ee77f42f1f0170b8b9e0dd81a93699d411","tid":2367604,"uid":114014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"搬⋯腳"},{"pid":"8a9646d00368c4e5b98f1a48321166e4f1fbb934","tid":2367604,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f65df65402148a38641218086559d25ece25e2e","tid":2367604,"uid":81505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"淘寶vs 去IG shop買淘寶貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a21a9a939197ac5fc117567036c41f652ba0033","tid":2367604,"uid":136311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"三贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸落到台 政治決定正確<br />\n澳洲賣到錢<br />\n其他國家過河濕腳又賺一畢"}]}